<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وع ر:</span> جَبَلٌ <span class="c2">(وَعْرٌ)</span> بِالتَّسْكِينِ وَمَطْلَبٌ وَعْرٌ.<span class="c5"> وَلَا تَقُلْ:</span> وَعِرٌ. وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(وَعُرَ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ <span class="c2">(وُعُورَةً)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(تَوَعَّرَ)</span> أَيْ صَارَ وَعْرًا. وَ <span class="c2">(وَعَّرَهُ)</span> غَيْرُهُ <span class="c2">(تَوْعِيرًا)</span> . <span class="c2">(وَاسْتَوْعَرَهُ)</span> وَجَدَهُ وَعْرًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>